no one will get hurt.

998
01:12:57,498 --> 01:13:00,751
How dare you make a joke
like that nowadays?

999
01:13:00,835 --> 01:13:03,880
Why don't you check upstairs first
then head to the basement?

1000
01:13:03,963 --> 01:13:05,798
